<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Commercial Greenery Systems | Lone Star Faux Scapes</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      /* Align to existing site palette */
      --bg-hero: #050a07;
      --bg-section: #0a140f;
      --bg-dark-green: #0f1a14;
      --text-main: #f5f5f5;
      --text-muted: #889990;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --accent: #4caf50;
      --accent-2: #74d680;
      --accent-3: #a3e6a8;
      --panel: rgba(5,10,7,0.82);
      --card-glass: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 15%, rgba(76,175,80,0.12), rgba(5,10,7,0.96));
      --shadow-strong: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      font-size: 17px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 10%, rgba(76,175,80,0.08) 0, transparent 42%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 86%, rgba(12,18,15,0.65) 0, var(--bg-hero) 55%),
        var(--bg-hero);
      color: var(--text-main);
      line-height: 1.65;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(5,10,7,0.75);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      transition: all 200ms ease;
    }
    header.scrolled {
      background: rgba(5,10,7,0.94);
      padding: 0.55rem 0;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.4rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .logo { font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; position: relative; }
    nav a { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; padding: 0.35rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; transition: color 150ms ease, background 150ms ease; }
    nav a:hover { color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
    .nav-group { position: relative; }
    .nav-group > a { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
    .nav-group .caret { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .nav-dropdown {
      position: absolute;
      top: 120%;
      left: 0;
      min-width: 200px;
      background: rgba(5,10,7,0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      padding: 8px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 4px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      z-index: 10;
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      transform: translateY(8px);
      transition: opacity 160ms ease, transform 160ms ease, visibility 160ms ease;
    }
    .nav-dropdown a { padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.92rem; color: #dce3d9; }
    .nav-dropdown a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
    .nav-group:hover .nav-dropdown { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; transform: translateY(0); }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2), var(--accent-3));
      color: #041208;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 1px rgba(34,197,94,0.3),
        0 18px 30px rgba(22,163,74,0.45);
      transition: transform 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease, filter 400ms ease-in-out;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px) scale(1.02); box-shadow: 0 24px 45px rgba(22,163,74,0.65); }
    .btn-ghost {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border 150ms ease, transform 150ms ease;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.45); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    main { overflow: hidden; }
    section { position: relative; }
    .section-wrap {
      max-width: 1280px;
      width: 94%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 72px 1.4rem;
    }
    .section-wrap.narrow { max-width: 1180px; }
    .hero {
      background:
        linear-gradient(115deg, rgba(5,10,7,0.82) 0%, rgba(5,10,7,0.55) 45%, rgba(5,10,7,0.68) 70%),
        url('images/commercial/commercial-2.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      padding: 90px 0 70px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% 20%, rgba(76,175,80,0.12), transparent 38%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .hero-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
      align-items: center;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .hero-visual { display:none; }
    .spec-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.16), rgba(255,255,255,0.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(125%);
      box-shadow:
        0 26px 70px rgba(0,0,0,0.38),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      isolation: isolate;
    }
    .spec-hero::after {
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.22), transparent 45%);
      opacity: 0.8;
      pointer-events:none;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .stat-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px,1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .stat-box {
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.22), rgba(255,255,255,0.08));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #0f130f;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }
    .stat-box span { display:block; color: #1f2b1f; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .spec-list { display:grid; gap: 8px; color:#0f130f; font-size:0.95rem; }
    .spec-list div { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.32); padding-bottom:6px; }
    .spec-list div:last-child { border-bottom:none; padding-bottom:0; }
    .spec-list span { color: #233226; }
    .quick-jump {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
    }
    .jump-pill {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: #d1d5db;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      transition: all 150ms ease;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .jump-pill.active { border-color: rgba(76,175,80,0.7); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
    h1 {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.25rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    h2 {
      font-family: "Space Grotesk", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 0 0 10px; font-family: "Space Grotesk", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; }
    p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .muted { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.98rem; }
    .hero .subcopy { max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 18px 0 12px; }
    .hero-bullets { margin: 12px 0 16px; padding: 0; list-style: none; display: grid; gap: 10px; }
    .hero-bullets li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #dce7dd; }
    .hero-bullets li::before { content: "•"; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-chips, .trust-points { display:none; }
    .stat-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .stat {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .stat strong { color: #fff; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .stat span { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .spec-card {
      background: var(--card-glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-strong);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .spec-card h3 { color: #fff; }
    .spec-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .spec-item {
      padding: 12px 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }
    .pill-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 10px 0 4px; }
    .pill { padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); font-size: 0.82rem; color: #cbd5e1; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    .systems { background: linear-gradient(var(--bg-hero), var(--bg-section)); }
    .process { background: linear-gradient(var(--bg-hero), var(--bg-dark-green)); }
    .cta-band { background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(76,175,80,0.22), rgba(5,10,7,0.9)); }
    .section-header { margin-bottom: 22px; }
    .section-lead { color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 720px; }
    .microcards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }
    .microcard {
      background: var(--card-glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .filters { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    .filter-pill {
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: #d1d5db;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      transition: all 150ms ease;
    }
    .filter-pill.active { border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.65); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(34,197,94,0.25), 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .card-thumb {
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .card-thumb img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      filter: brightness(0.78);
      transition: transform 800ms ease;
    }
    .card:hover .card-thumb img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .card {
      background: var(--card-glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.32);
      transition: transform 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease, border-image 180ms ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #2dd4bf) 1;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    }
    .card .meta { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin:6px 0 6px; }
    .card .meta .chip { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding:6px 10px; border-radius:999px; font-size:0.82rem; color:#d1d5db; }
    .spec-strip {
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #c7d0c9;
    }
    .spec-strip span {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .hover-spec {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(8px);
      transition: opacity 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .card:hover .hover-spec { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .card .icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(34,197,94,0.14);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: #a3e635;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .tag {
      position: absolute;
      top: 14px;
      right: 14px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }
    .timeline {
      position: relative;
      padding-top: 18px;
    }
    .timeline-line {
      position: absolute;
      top: 36px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(76,175,80,0.35), rgba(116,214,128,0.2));
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
    .process-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .process-card { padding: 18px; min-height: 150px; }
    .step { font-weight: 700; color: #bef264; margin-bottom: 6px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; }
    .divider {
      width: 100%;
      height: 70px;
      background: linear-gradient(100deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0, rgba(255,255,255,0.008) 70%, transparent 100%);
      transform: skewY(-2deg);
      margin: -10px 0 -30px;
    }
    .projects-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .flip {
      perspective: 1000px;
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 360px;
    }
    .flip-inner {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      transition: transform 500ms ease;
      transform-style: preserve-3d;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }
    .flip:hover .flip-inner { transform: rotateY(180deg); }
    .flip-face {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      backface-visibility: hidden;
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: grid;
      place-items: end;
      padding: 16px;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .flip-face.back {
      transform: rotateY(180deg);
      background: var(--card-glass);
      align-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .flip img {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      filter: brightness(0.7);
      transition: transform 3s ease;
    }
    .flip:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .overlay {
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 45%, rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .overlay h3 { margin: 0; }
    .cities {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .map-card {
      position: relative;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(76,175,80,0.14), transparent 55%), radial-gradient(circle at 75% 70%, rgba(12,18,15,0.8), rgba(5,10,7,0.9));
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .map-pin {
      position: absolute;
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(76,175,80,0.6);
    }
    .map-pin::after {
      content: attr(data-city);
      position: absolute;
      top: -8px;
      left: 16px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #d1d5db;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .city-bar {
      background: var(--card-glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 12px;
    }
    .bar-track {
      width: 100%;
      height: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      width: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(34,197,94,0.6);
      transition: width 900ms ease;
    }
    .faq-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px,1fr)); gap:10px; }
    details {
      background: var(--card-glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      min-height: 56px;
    }
    details + details { margin-top: 0; }
    summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 700;
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-icon {
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    details ul { margin: 8px 0 4px 16px; padding:0; color: var(--text-muted); }
    details ul li { margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .cta-panel {
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(34,197,94,0.28), rgba(2,44,34,0.95));
      border: 1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.28);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; padding: 28px 1rem 40px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .io-reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); transition: opacity 420ms ease, transform 420ms ease; }
    .io-reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .hero-cta.breathe { animation: breathe 3.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes breathe {
      0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(34,197,94,0.35); }
      50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(34,197,94,0.0); }
      100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(34,197,94,0.0); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-inner { flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .hero { padding-top: 60px; }
      .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .spec-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cta-panel { padding: 22px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header id="site-header">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <div class="logo">LONE STAR FAUX SCAPES</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="products.html">Products</a>
        <div class="nav-group">
          <a href="commercial.html" aria-current="page">Commercial <span class="caret">▾</span></a>
          <div class="nav-dropdown">
            <a href="hedge-builder-commercial.html">Hedge Builder</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-group">
          <a href="residential.html">Residential <span class="caret">▾</span></a>
          <div class="nav-dropdown">
            <a href="hedge-builder-residential.html">Hedge Builder</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="btn-primary" style="padding:0.6rem 1.2rem;">Start a project</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="section-wrap hero-grid io-reveal" id="top">
        <div>
          <h1>Fire-rated greenery for commercial builds.</h1>
          <p class="subcopy">Code-safe, acoustic, and UV-stable systems with shop drawings and rapid install crews.</p>
